To open the Simple Browser in Cursor:

1. Press **Cmd+Shift+P** (or Ctrl+Shift+P on Windows/Linux)
2. Type **"Simple Browser: Show"** and select it
3. Enter the URL: `http://localhost:5173/`

Alternatively, you can simply **Cmd+click** (or Ctrl+click) on this link: http://localhost:5173/

This will open the app directly in Cursor's built-in browser panel.
